subject: United States Open (Tennis)
Tennis
lead_paragraph: Jo-Wilfried Tsonga could not get past Martin Klizan and fell in the biggest upset on the men’s side so far, while Mardy Fish lost the first two sets against Nikolay Davydenko before winning in five.
